sentence: While goal-conditioning methods can address the suboptimality of adapting model-free methods to test-time data by serving as the representation for the test-time reward function, the goal space of the agents must be specified a priori, requires goal labels, and precludes adapting the learned system to new types of test-time goal objectives .
